Package: scale-guinstall
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10) | python3.11 | python3.12 | python3.13, python3-venv
Recommends: python3-pip
Maintainer: cdmaestas <cdmaestas@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/cdmaestas/Scale-GUInstall
Description: IBM Storage Scale Installation Toolkit GUI backend
 Scale GUInstall provides a web-based GUI for the IBM Storage Scale
 Installation Toolkit (spectrumscale). This package installs the Flask
 backend server that the GUI connects to for live command execution.
 .
 Open Scale-GUInstall.html in a browser on your workstation, establish
 an SSH tunnel to this node (ssh -L 5001:127.0.0.1:5001 user@this-node),
 and the GUI will connect automatically.
 .
 The server binds to 127.0.0.1 only and is not accessible from the network
 without an SSH tunnel.
